# Crop Land Classification using Hybrid Quantum Machine Learning

## Overview
This project classifies crop land from satellite imagery using a Hybrid Quantum Machine Learning approach.

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Qiskit
- Scikit-learn
- Pandas
- NumPy
- React
- Flask

## Features
- Satellite image preprocessing
- Feature extraction
- Crop land classification
- Hybrid Quantum Machine Learning
- Interactive web interface

## Dataset
Dataset Source:
https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/apollo2506/eurosat-dataset

The dataset is not included in this repository because of its large size.


## Future Improvements
- Improve model accuracy
- Add more satellite datasets
- Deploy on cloud platforms
